description:
Voting is now open for the 2012 Golden Crocoduck. Please go to http://www.crocoduck.org.uk/ to cast your vote. My thanks to BeforeTheNoose for setting this up, as he does every year. The page really looks good.
   The coveted Golden Crocoduck is awarded every year for the biggest breach of the 9th Commandment in pursuit of the creationist cause.
   Nominations are now open for the 2013 Golden Crocoduck. But here are some ground rules:
   1) Please do not send me videos of creationists expounding their beliefs or saying evolution is nonsense or any other kind of opinion. See (above) what the award is for.
   2) Please give me a link to the video, describe the nature of the breach, and tell me where it can be found on the video. Nominations that just say 'watch this' have a very slim chance of being watched or ending up in the nominations playlist.

"One Atheist's Creed" can be found at: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GCiLVCEqnRg

MUSIC:
"Crazy" by Patsy Cline
"Blackwaterside" by Fairport Convention
